videos.headline: Sirk's TD pass gets East Carolina on the board first
videos.description: Thomas Sirk finds Davon Grayson in the end zone for a 17-yard touchdown pass.

videos.headline: Donaldson's first collegiate reception goes for 45-yard UConn TD
videos.description: Bryant Shirreffs finds a wide-open Mason Donaldson for a long touchdown for Connecticut's first score

videos.headline: Scott's TD pads East Carolina's lead
videos.description: Derrell Scott runs for a 6-yard touchdown to add to East Carolina's leads over UConn

videos.headline: UConn chips away at East Carolina's lead with TD
videos.description: Nate Hopkins gets UConn closer to East Carolina's lead with a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: East Carolina throws long TD on first play of the second half
videos.description: Thomas Sirk passes to Davon Grayson for an impressive 75-yard touchdown for East Carolina.

videos.headline: UConn's Newsome scores his first TD of the day
videos.description: Arkeel Newsome runs for an 8-yard touchdown to help the Huskies cut into the  to the Pirates' lead.

videos.headline: Shirreffs connects with Donaldson for 2nd TD
videos.description: Bryant Shirreffs passes to Mason Donaldson for a 12-yard touchdown to put the Huskies on the board in the second half.

videos.headline: UConn cuts into deficit with 79-yard TD
videos.description: Bryant Shirreffs finds Arkeel Newsome for a long touchdown, cutting into East Carolina's lead to 41-38.
